subtitleNullable: Share Price of India's COVAXIN vaccine manufacturer
descriptionNullable:
### Context

COVID has changed our lives. With millions affected this has been an time when many companies had to change the wa,y they do business to survive.
This pandemic has in a way boosted the India Pharma - with India developing two vaccines to fight this Pandemic. 

### Content

This dataset contains the share price of Bharat Biotech since 2000- India's indigenous COVID-19 vaccine COVAXIN® manufacturer, developed in collaboration with the Indian Council of Medical Research (ICMR) - National Institute of Virology (NIV).


### Acknowledgements

This data has been collected from Yahoo Finance(https://finance.yahoo.com/quote/BIBCL.BO/history?p=BIBCL.BO)
